					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Cosmic Spacehead has region detection.<br />In NTSC mode, the game runs at normal speed.<br />In PAL mode, it alternates between running 1 frame of game logic and running 2 frames of game logic, for an effective game speed of 75FPS.<br />In Dendy mode, the game is unplayable with servere graphics glitches since the game thinks it's a PAL console.</div>

					
